<lb n="0578a11"/><head type="no">No. 1135</head>
<lb n="0578a12"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0578001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等校訂加筆本</note>佛說一切如來金剛壽命陀羅尼
<lb n="0578a13"/>經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0578a14"/>
<lb n="0578a15"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0578002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（開府…空）四十三字＝（南天竺國三藏金剛智共沙門智藏）十四字【宋】【元】，（唐南天竺國三藏金剛智共沙門智藏）十五字【明】【甲】</note><note n="0578002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（開府…空）四十三字＝（南天竺國三藏金剛智共沙門智藏）十四字【宋】【元】，＝（唐南天竺國三藏金剛智共沙門智藏）十五字【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578002" word-count="43"><lem>開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0578a16"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑑
<lb n="0578a17"/>正號大廣智大興善寺三藏沙門
<lb n="0578a18"/>不空</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">南天竺國三藏金剛智共沙門智藏</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">唐南天竺國三藏金剛智共沙門智藏</rdg></app>奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0578a19"/><div1 type="jing"><p>如是我聞。一時佛<note n="0578003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">在＝住【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">在＝住【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578003"><lem>在</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">住</rdg></app>殑伽河側。與諸比丘及
<lb n="0578a20"/>大菩薩無量天人大眾俱。爾時世尊告毘沙
<lb n="0578a21"/>門等四天王言。有四種法甚可怖畏。若男若
<lb n="0578a22"/>女童男童女。一切有情無能免者。所謂生老
<lb n="0578a23"/>病死。於中一法最為<note n="0578004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遍＝逼【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遍＝逼【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578004"><lem>遍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">逼</rdg></app>惱。難可對治。所謂
<lb n="0578a24"/>死怖。我愍是故說對治法。爾時四天王白佛
<lb n="0578a25"/>言。世尊我於今日為獲大利。<note n="0578005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578005"><lem>唯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">惟</rdg></app>願世尊為眾
<lb n="0578a26"/>生故宣說是法。爾時世尊面向東方。彈指召
<lb n="0578a27"/>集一切如來。作是誓言。所有十方一切如來
<lb n="0578a28"/>應正等覺。為眾生故。證菩提者咸皆助我。令
<lb n="0578a29"/>我以一切如來威神力故。悉<note n="0578006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">令＋（如是）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">令＋（如是）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578006"><lem>令</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">令如是</rdg></app>一切眾生轉
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1135.0578b" n="0578b"/>
<lb n="0578b01"/>非命業。使增壽命。我昔未為眾生轉此法輪。
<lb n="0578b02"/>於今方轉。能令眾生壽命色力皆得成就無
<lb n="0578b03"/>夭死怖。如是南西北方四維上下。召集<note n="0578007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">驚＝警【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">驚＝警【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578007"><lem>驚</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">警</rdg></app>告
<lb n="0578b04"/>亦復如是。爾時十方盡佛眼所到。若干世界
<lb n="0578b05"/>一切如來皆悉赴集。遍滿虛空數如微塵。爾
<lb n="0578b06"/>時一切諸佛為加持故。異口同音。即說一切
<lb n="0578b07"/>如來金剛壽命陀羅尼曰</p>
<lb n="0578b08"/><p type="dharani">怛<note n="0578008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">胵＝&CB00135;也二合去引【宋】【元】，&CB00135;也去聲二合引【明】【甲】</note><note n="0578008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">胵＝&CB00135;也二合去引【宋】【元】，＝&CB00135;也去聲二合引【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578008"><lem>胵</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&CB00135;也二合去引</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00135;也去聲二合引</rdg></app>他<note place="inline">一</note>者犁<note place="inline">二</note>者<note n="0578009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00256;＋（引）細註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00256;＋（引）細註【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578009"><lem>&CB00256;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00256;<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app>者犁<note place="inline">三</note><note n="0578010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">彌娜知＝尾娜胝【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">彌娜知＝尾娜胝【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578010"><lem>彌娜知</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">尾娜胝</rdg></app>薩&CB00085;
<lb n="0578b09"/><note place="inline">二合</note>薩底<note place="inline">二合</note>稽<note place="inline">四</note>斫訖浪<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00617;<note n="0578011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">南＝喃【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0578011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">南＝喃【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0578011"><lem>南</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">喃</rdg></app><note place="inline">五</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0578b10"/>舍滿<note n="0578012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">都＋（六）細註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">都＋（六）細註【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578012"><lem>都</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">都<note place="inline">六</note></rdg></app>薩<note n="0578013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婆路&CB00344;六薩婆＝&CB00085;路引&CB00344;薩&CB00085;【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婆路&CB00344;六薩婆＝&CB00085;路引&CB00344;薩&CB00085;【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578013"><lem>婆路&CB00344;<note place="inline">六</note>薩婆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00085;路引&CB00344;薩&CB00085;</rdg></app>薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note><app type="＊" source="0578011"><lem>南</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">喃</rdg></app><note place="inline">七</note>
<lb n="0578b11"/>阿娜<note n="0578014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03868;＝&CB00600;知解反八【宋】【元】，&CB00600;知解切八【明】【甲】</note><note n="0578014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB03868;＝&CB00600;知解反八【宋】【元】，＝&CB00600;知解切八【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578014"><lem>&CB03868;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&CB00600;知解反八</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00600;知解切八</rdg></app><note place="inline">八</note>俱娜&CB00600;<note place="inline">九</note><note n="0578015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（遮&CB00942;…反）十一字＝（摩賀娜&CB00600;十者&CB00942;者&CB00942;係麼澆）十二字【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（遮&CB00942;…反）十一字＝（摩賀娜&CB00600;十者&CB00942;者&CB00942;係麼澆）十二字【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578015" word-count="11"><lem>遮&CB00942;遮&CB00942;<note place="inline">十</note>係麼澆<note place="inline">牛矯反</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">摩賀娜&CB00600;十者&CB00942;者&CB00942;係麼澆</rdg></app>
<lb n="0578b12"/>哩<note place="inline">十一</note>係麼&CB00135;鏟<note n="0578016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尼＋（去）細註【宋】【元】，（去聲）細註【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578016"><lem>尼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">尼<note place="inline">去</note></rdg><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">尼<note place="inline">去聲</note></rdg></app><note place="inline">十二</note>係麼尸棄<note place="inline">十三</note>矯囉微
<lb n="0578b13"/><note place="inline">十四</note>矯囉<note n="0578017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">迷＝&CB00734;【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">迷＝&CB00734;【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578017"><lem>迷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00734;</rdg></app><note place="inline">十五</note>係俱囉微<note place="inline">十六</note>信囉&CB02740;<note place="inline">十七</note>俱
<lb n="0578b14"/>麼底<note place="inline">十八</note>微捨麼<note n="0578018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">抳＋（麼抳）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">抳＋（麼抳）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578018"><lem>抳</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">抳麼抳</rdg></app><note place="inline">十九</note><note n="0578019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">戍戍＝戌戌【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">戍戍＝戌戌【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578019"><lem>戍戍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">戌戌</rdg></app><note n="0578020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">毘＋（引）細註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">毘＋（引）細註【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578020"><lem>毘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">毘<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二十</note>阿者
<lb n="0578b15"/>犁<note place="inline">二十一</note>彌者犁<note place="inline">二十二</note>麼尾<note n="0578021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">覽＝&CB00772;【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">覽＝&CB00772;【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578021"><lem>覽</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00772;</rdg></app>麼<note place="inline">二十三</note>戶<note n="0578022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">毛＝&CB02802;【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0578022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">毛＝&CB02802;【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0578022"><lem>毛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB02802;</rdg></app>戶
<lb n="0578b16"/><app type="＊" source="0578022"><lem>毛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&CB02802;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二十四</note>唵<note n="0578023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二十五麼折囉＝&CB00085;曰囉二合【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二十五麼折囉＝&CB00085;曰囉二合【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578023"><lem><note place="inline">二十五</note>麼折囉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00085;曰囉二合</rdg></app>諭<note n="0578024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">師＝曬【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">師＝曬【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578024"><lem>師</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">曬</rdg></app><note place="inline">某甲<note n="0578025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二十六〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔二十六〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578025"><lem>二十六</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>薩&CB00085;
<lb n="0578b17"/><note n="0578026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＝二合賀引二十五【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶＝二合賀引二十五【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578026"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">二合賀引二十五</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0578b18"/><p>爾時十方佛所。一切執金剛菩薩異口同音
<lb n="0578b19"/>亦說延命陀羅尼曰</p>
<lb n="0578b20"/><p type="dharani">吽<note n="0578027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0578027" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>〔引〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0578027"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>吽<note place="inline">引</note>尸棄薩&CB00085;<note place="inline"><note n="0578028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二合引＝引二合【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二合引＝引二合【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578028"><lem>二合引</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">引二合</rdg></app></note><note n="0578029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶引＝賀一引【宋】，賀引【元】，賀引一【明】【甲】</note><note n="0578029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶引＝賀一引【宋】，＝賀引【元】，＝賀引一【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578029"><lem>訶<note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">賀一引</rdg><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">賀引</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">賀引一</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0578b21"/><p>如是一切如來及十方執金剛菩薩。說是陀
<lb n="0578b22"/>羅尼已隱而不現</p>
<lb n="0578b23"/><p>爾時毘沙門天王白佛言。我<note n="0578030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔亦〕－【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0578030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔亦〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0578030"><lem>亦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>以佛神力。為
<lb n="0578b24"/>一切眾生加持護念。除非命故說陀羅<note n="0578031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尼＋（曰）【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0578031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尼＋（曰）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0578031"><lem>尼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">尼曰</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0578b25"/><p type="dharani">始尾<note place="inline">二合<note n="0578032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔下同〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔下同〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578032"><lem>下同</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>帝<note place="inline">一</note>始<note n="0578033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尾＋（二合）細註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尾＋（二合）細註【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578033"><lem>尾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">尾<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>怛犁<note place="inline">二</note>栗<note n="0578034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">利＋（三）細註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">利＋（三）細註【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578034"><lem>利</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">利<note place="inline">三</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0578b26"/><p>爾時毘樓勒叉天王又白佛言。我<app type="＊" source="0578030"><lem>亦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>以佛神
<lb n="0578b27"/><note n="0578035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">力＋（故）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">力＋（故）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578035"><lem>力</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">力故</rdg></app>。為多眾生除夭命故。說陀<note n="0578036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉＝羅【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578036"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0578031"><lem>尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">尼曰</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0578b28"/><p type="dharani">摩<note n="0578037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">登＝蹬【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">登＝蹬【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578037"><lem>登</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">蹬</rdg></app>霓<note n="0578038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578038"><lem><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>摩<note n="0578039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">登儗尼二＝蹬倪尼一【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">登儗尼二＝蹬倪尼一【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578039"><lem>登儗尼<note place="inline">二</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">蹬倪尼一</rdg></app>輸<note n="0578040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">麼輸麼＝摩輸【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">麼輸麼＝摩輸【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578040"><lem>麼輸麼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">摩輸</rdg></app>謀<note place="inline"><note n="0578041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝二【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三＝二【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578041"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0578b29"/><p>爾時提頭賴吒天王亦白佛言。我亦為諸眾
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1135.0578c" n="0578c"/>
<lb n="0578c01"/>生。除死怖故說陀羅<app type="＊" source="0578031"><lem>尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">尼曰</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0578c02"/><p type="dharani">者&CB01238;者&CB01238;<note place="inline">一</note>者囉<note n="0578042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02740;＝哩引二【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB02740;＝哩引二【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578042"><lem>&CB02740;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">哩引二</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0578c03"/><p>爾時毘樓博叉天王亦白佛言。我亦以佛神
<lb n="0578c04"/>力故。令一切眾生除非命故說陀羅<app type="＊" source="0578031"><lem>尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">尼曰</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0578c05"/><p type="dharani">未臨<note place="inline">一</note><note n="0578043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">麼麼麼＝&CB00085;&CB00085;&CB00085;&CB00085;二【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">麼麼麼＝&CB00085;&CB00085;&CB00085;&CB00085;二【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578043"><lem>麼麼麼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00085;&CB00085;&CB00085;&CB00085;二</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0578c06"/><p>佛告四天王言。若有讀誦此經。日日受持乃
<lb n="0578c07"/>至一遍。<note n="0578044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＋（應）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當＋（應）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578044"><lem>當</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">當應</rdg></app>敬彼善男子善女人。應如佛想終
<lb n="0578c08"/>不墮三惡道定增壽命。若人每日。為一切眾
<lb n="0578c09"/>生轉<note n="0578045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">讀＝誦【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">讀＝誦【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578045"><lem>讀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">誦</rdg></app>此經。終無夭死短命之怖。亦無惡夢
<lb n="0578c10"/>魘魅&CB00057;。<note n="0578046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">咀＝詛【三】【甲】</note><note n="0578046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">咀＝詛【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0578046"><lem>咀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">詛</rdg></app>惡形羅剎鬼神之怖。亦不為水火
<lb n="0578c11"/>兵毒之所傷害。一切諸佛菩薩攝受護念其
<lb n="0578c12"/>處。亦為佛所護持。爾時世尊說是經已。毘沙
<lb n="0578c13"/>門天王等一切大眾。皆大歡喜信受奉行</p>
<lb n="0578c14"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><note n="0578047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】</note><app n="0578047"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>一切如來金剛壽命陀羅尼經<note n="0578048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下甲本奧書曰貞享三年九月十七日點校了淨嚴四十八載，元祿十六年正月二十九日以淨嚴和上之本再校了尊教</note></jhead></juan></div1>
